OL,3,CInflation falls to 3% boosting
OL,4,Cexpectations of interest rate cut
OL,6,FInflation fell from 3.4% to 3% in
OL,7,FJanuary, its lowest level in 10
OL,8,Fmonths, off the back of falling petrol
OL,9,Fprices and slower food price
OL,10,Fincreases, the Office for National
OL,11,FStatistics (ONS) has said.
OL,13,FThe rate of Consumer Prices Index
OL,14,F(CPI) inflation decreased to 3% in
OL,15,FJanuary from 3.4% in December, which
OL,16,Fwas in line with economists'
OL,17,Fpredictions.
