OL,3,CInflation falls to 3% boosting
OL,4,Cexpectations of interest rate cut
OL,6,FData showed that motor fuels
OL,7,Fparticularly contributed to the fall
OL,8,Fof inflation, with the average price
OL,9,Fof petrol falling by 3.1p per litre
OL,10,Fbetween December 2025 and January 2026.
OL,12,FONS chief economist Grant Fitzner
OL,13,Fsaid: "Airfares were another downward
OL,14,Fdriver this month with prices dropping
OL,15,Fback following the increase in
OL,16,FDecember.
OL,18,F"Lower food prices also helped push
OL,19,Fthe rate down, particularly for bread
OL,20,F& cereals and meat.
