OL,3,CInflation falls to 3% boosting
OL,4,Cexpectations of interest rate cut
OL,6,F"These were partially offset by the
OL,7,Fcost of hotel stays and takeaways."
OL,9,FThe figures are likely to reinforce
OL,10,Fexpectations of another interest rate
OL,11,Fcut, possibly as soon as next month.
OL,13,FDisappointing growth figures for the
OL,14,Ffinal quarter of last year have added
OL,15,Fto forecasts for a rate cut in March,
OL,16,Fto 3.5% from 3.75% currently.
