OL,3,CInflation falls to 3% boosting
OL,4,Cexpectations of interest rate cut
OL,6,FThe ONS said gross domestic product
OL,7,F(GDP) eked a meagre growth of 0.1% in
OL,8,Fthe fourth quarter of 2025, leaving
OL,9,Fthe out-turn for the year as a whole
OL,10,Fat a worse-than-expected 1.3%
OL,11,Fexpansion.
OL,13,FOfficial figures on Tuesday showing
OL,14,Fwage growth fell back once again to is
OL,15,Flowest level for almost four years,
OL,16,Fhave also boosted the argument for
OL,17,Flowering interest rates.
