OL,3,CInflation falls to 3% boosting
OL,4,Cexpectations of interest rate cut
OL,6,FThe Bank of England is forecasting
OL,7,Fthat inflation will fall to its 2%
OL,8,Ftarget by the middle of the year, as
OL,9,Fmeasures announced in the Chancellor's
OL,10,Fautumn budget will help to slow
OL,11,Finflation, particularly a package of
OL,12,Fsupport to bring down household energy
OL,13,Fbills from April.
OL,15,FIn response to the new inflation
OL,16,Ffigures, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,17,Fsaid: "Cutting the cost of living is
OL,18,Fmy number one priority.
